import flet as ft

ft.Draggable()


class DesignerSections(ft.UserControl):
    def __init__(self):
        super().__init__()

    def build(self):
        self.PreviewSection = ft.DragTarget(
            group="widget",
            content=ft.Container(
                width=1200,
                height=1000,
                border=ft.border.all(3, color=ft.colors.CYAN_300),
                border_radius=ft.border_radius.all(10),
                bgcolor=ft.colors.BLACK12,
                margin=ft.margin.only(left=100, top=25),
            ),
        )

        return self.PreviewSection
